" jk and kj -> Quit Insert mode (and autosave)
" inoremap jk <Esc><Esc>`^:w<Cr>
" inoremap kj <Esc><Esc>`^:w<Cr>
inoremap jk <Esc><Esc>`^
inoremap kj <Esc><Esc>`^
cnoremap jk <C-c>
cnoremap kj <C-c>
set ideajoin

" Easier marks:
"  Set marks with "ma" "mb" etc and jump back to them with "mma" "mmb" etc
nnoremap mm `
vnoremap mm `

let mapleader = "\<Space>"

